        "collapsible_row_8aQjkK": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you ship globally?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, we proudly offer at-cost international shipping to most countries worldwide. However, there are a few exceptions where we are currently unable to deliver.</p><p>We ship to:</p><p>United States, Canada, United Kingdom, France, Germany, Italy, Spain, Australia, New Zealand, Russia, Qatar, United Arab Emirates, China, Taiwan (China), Hong Kong (China), Singapore, Japan, South Korea, Malaysia, Thailand, Vietnam</p>",
            "media_ratio": "fit",
            "media_width": 50
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FHGiNX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long will it take to get my order?",
            "content": "<p>We strive to process and ship orders as quickly as possible - typically within 2 business days.</p><p><br/>Delivery Times<br/>We do our best to ensure timely delivery for all orders. Please note that all delivery dates are estimated and provided directly by the carrier.</p><p><br/>Estimated delivery time by area:</p><p>Americas: 5–10 business days</p><p>Asia: 5–10 business days</p><p>Europe: 7–15 business days</p><p><br/>Tracking Your Order<br/>Once your order ships, you’ll receive a confirmation email with tracking details. If you have questions about your package’s location after shipment, please contact the shipping carrier directly, as we do not have access to packages once they leave our warehouse.<br/><br/>Signature<br/>A signature is required upon delivery for orders that do not select package insurance. If no one is available to sign, the carrier will leave a notice to arrange redelivery or pickup.</p>",
            "media_ratio": "fit",
            "media_width": 50
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_DUQ4MT": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is a signature required?",
            "content": "<p>A signature is required upon delivery for orders that do not select package insurance at checkout. If no one is available to sign, the carrier will leave a notice to arrange redelivery or pickup.</p>",
            "media_ratio": "fit",
            "media_width": 50
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_wFXB8G": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is shipping insurance offered?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. We have partnered with a third-party insurance company to offer you protection against, loss, theft and damage during shipping. Insurance can be selected at checkout. Please note: <strong>PSN is not responsible for packages lost or stolen during transit.</strong></p>",
            "media_ratio": "fit",
            "media_width": 50
          }
        }
      },
